    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Amynthas gageodo sp. nov., holotype showing prostomium, ventral view of body with spermathecae and prostates in situ (genital markings nearby), posterior pygidium, and intestinal caecum in 27; plus an enlargement of 6lhs (left-hand-side) spermatheca." ;
